data.description: A summer retreat or year-round home? You decide.  Totally renovated 2 bedroom, 2 bath cottage with many unique features and a great water view.   Cozy, but with a touch of class.  Whip up your favorite meals in the custom kitchen.  Sit in your living room or on front porch and enjoy the colorful flowers and water view.  Relax or swim in your jet tub spa or cozy up to the fireplace when there is a nip in the air.   Enjoy the cost savings of the installed solar panel system.   Big yard in front and back provides plenty of space to garden, play or just amble about.  Community pier and St. Clements Museum are just a block away.   Come, see, enjoy.  It could be yours!
